            intentionally gather Personal Information from individuals who are
            under the age of 16. If you believe that we might have any
            information from a child under age 16 without consent of a parent or
            guardian, please contact us at. If we learn that we have
            inadvertently collected the Personal Information of a child under 16
            without proper consent, or equivalent minimum age depending on
            jurisdiction, we will take steps to delete the information as soon
            as possible.
