          <p>
            <span style="font-weight: bold"
              >Right to Limit Use and Disclosure of Sensitive Personal
              Information.</span
            >
            We do not collect Sensitive Personal Information.
          </p>
          <p>
            <span style="font-weight: bold">Right to Correction.</span> You have
            the right to request that we maintain accurate Personal Information
            about you and correct any Personal Information about you which we
            have collected from you, subject to exceptions within the law. You
            may exercise your right to correction by emailing
            <a href="hello@getflair.io">hello@getflair.io</a>.
          </p>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 0">
            <span style="font-weight: bold">Non-Discrimination.</span> We may
